I added a CSP in the previous turn to improve security, but I missed whitelisting the aistudiocdn.com domain. Since the application loads React, Firebase, and other dependencies via an importmap pointing to https://aistudiocdn.com, the browser is currently blocking all these scripts, causing the app to crash immediately on load.
